{
  "chapter": 35,
  "chapter_summary": "傅红雪在面摊遇见一位洁净英俊却极其危险的陌生人，二人围绕杀气、杀人的理由与拔刀生死反复试探。陌生人感到傅红雪杀意，却始终从容，甚至劝他不要无故杀人。紧要关头叶开赶到，为傅红雪向陌生人解释其杀人的理由值得原谅，陌生人遂离去。丁灵琳赠铃，铃声与短棍显出其神秘身手。叶开随后告诉傅红雪，此人正是阿飞，短棍在他手中已胜过剑，只有小李飞刀或能更快；又揭破地上“金疯子”实为京城名伶小达子，一切乃易大经“双圈套”剧本。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "请坐。\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "请坐。\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "喝酒？\"",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "不喝。\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "从来不喝？\"",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "现在不喝。\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "十年了……\"",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "十年来，已没有人想杀死我。\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "但你现在却是来杀我的！\n\"",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "是不是？\"",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "是！\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "我看得出你是个不会说谎的人。\"",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "不会说谎，但却会杀人。\"",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "你杀过很多人？\"",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "不少。\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "你觉得杀人很有趣？\"",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "我杀人并不是为了觉得有趣。\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "是为了什么？\"",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "我不必告诉你。\"",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "不错，每个人杀人都有他自己的理由，的确不必告诉别人。\n\"",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "你怎知我要来杀你？\"",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "你有杀气。\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "你看得出？\"",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "杀气是看不出来的，但却有种人能感觉得到。\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "你就是这种人？\"",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "我是的。\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "就因为我有这种感觉，所以现在我还活着。\n\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "现在你的确还活着。\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "你认为你一定可以杀死我？\"",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "世上没有杀不死的人。\"",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "你有把握？\"",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "没有把握，就不会来。\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "我喜欢你这个人。\"",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "但我还是要杀你。\"",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "为什么？\"",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "没有原因。\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "没有原因也杀人？\"",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "就算有原因，也不能告诉你。\n\"",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "你是不是非杀我不可？\"",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "是。\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "可惜。\"",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "可惜？\"",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "我已有多年未杀人。\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "哦？\"",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "那只因我有个原则，你若不想杀我，我也绝不杀你。\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "我若定要杀你呢？\"",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "你就得死。\"",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "死的也许是你。\"",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "也许是……\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "看来你的刀一定很快？\n\"",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "够快的。\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "很好。\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "杀人并不是件有趣的事，被杀更无趣。\n\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "我一向不喜欢没有原因就想杀人的人，尤其是年轻人，年轻人不该养成这种习惯的。\n\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "我也不是来听你教训的。\"",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "刀在你手里，你随时都可以拔出来。\"",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "他是你的朋友？\"",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "是的。\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "他是个怎么样的人？\"",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "是个很容易上当的人。\"",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "是不是随便杀人的人？\"",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "绝不是。\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "他有理由要杀我？\"",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "有。\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 272
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "是不是个很好的理由？\"",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "不是，但却是个值得原谅的理由。\"",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 276
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "好，这就够了。\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "我知道你喜欢请客，今天我让你请一次。\n\"",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 282
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "谢谢你。\"",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
